Theme Description <code>default</code> Neutral, Tableau 10 palette, transparent background <code>dark</code> Dark background, cool palette <code>bootstrap</code> Matches Bootstrap 5 colors <code>terraf</code> Earth tones, DM Sans font <pre><code>chart = BarChart(data=data, x="x", y="y", theme="dark")
</code></pre> <p>Or override in the template:</p> <pre><code>{% d3_render chart theme="bootstrap" %}
</code></pre>
